rescuecore2.misc.gui

Class ListModelList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.AbstractListModel
      • rescuecore2.misc.gui.ListModelList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of object that lives in this list.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>, javax.swing.ListModel

    public class ListModelList<T>
extends javax.swing.AbstractListModel
implements java.util.List<T>, javax.swing.ListModel
    A java.util.List implementation that also implements javax.swing.ListModel. This class delegates to a real list for storing data.
